    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offering a superlative example of the E46 M3, featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six power plant. This vehicle exhibits exceptional mechanical integrity, with the high-pressure Vanos system and individual throttle bodies operating in perfect synchronicity. It has been meticulously maintained with documented rod bearing replacement and a reinforced rear subframe to ensure structural rigidity. The Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox provides crisp, tactile engagement, paired with a factory-spec limited-slip differential for optimal torque vectoring. The exterior retains full paint depth with no signs of oxidation, while the cabin remains a time capsule, free of bolster wear or dash delamination. This is a turn-key, collector-grade chassis optimized for peak lateral acceleration and linear power delivery.",
